spec_data.Name: php-doctrine-datafixtures
spec_data.Description:
This extension aims to provide a simple way to manage and execute the loading
of data fixtures for the Doctrine ORM or ODM.

Autoloader: /usr/share/php/Doctrine/Common/DataFixtures/autoload.php
